{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77e40578-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460ll–1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"460ll–1"},"text":"§ 460ll–1.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Rattlesnake Wilderness","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77e40579-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460ll–1/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Designation of area","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In furtherance of the purposes of the Wilderness Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/78/890"},"text":"78 Stat. 890","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1131"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 1131","children":[],"tail":"), certain lands within the Rattlesnake National Recreation Area as designated by this subchapter, which comprise approximately 33,000 acres as generally depicted as the “Rattlesnake Wilderness” on a map entitled “Rattlesnake National Recreation Area and Wilderness—Proposed”, and dated "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 1980","children":[],"tail":", are hereby designated as wilderness and shall be known as the Rattlesnake Wilderness."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77e4057a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460ll–1/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Administration","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subject to valid existing rights, the Rattle­snake Wilderness as designated by this subchapter shall be administered by the Secretary of Agriculture, hereafter referred to as the Secretary, in accordance with the provisions of the Wilderness Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1131"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 1131","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] governing areas designated by that Act as wilderness: "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That any reference in such provisions to the effective date of the Wilderness Act shall be deemed to be a reference to the effective date of this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77e4057b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/476/s2"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–476, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-19"},"text":"Oct. 19, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2271"},"text":"94 Stat. 2271","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77e4057c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77e4057d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77e4057e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Wilderness Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–577","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1964","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/78/890"},"text":"78 Stat. 890","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 23 (§ 1131 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1131"},"text":"section 1131 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The effective date of the Wilderness Act, referred to in subsec. (b), means ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1964","children":[],"tail":", the date of enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–577","children":[],"tail":", which enacted chapter 23 of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The effective date of this subchapter, referred to in subsec. (b), means ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-19"},"text":"Oct. 19, 1980","children":[],"tail":", the date of enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/476"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–476","children":[],"tail":", which enacted this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
